%p
  %em Custom Commander
  also known as
  %em Custom EDH
  is a custom eternal Constructed multiplayer format modeled after <a href="commander">Commander</a>.

%p
  Decks consist of 100 cards and no sideboard, one of which is a legendary creature chosen as a commander.

%p
  Except for basic lands, all cards are allowed in only 1 copy. No card is allowed if its color identity contains colors outside color identity of the chosen commander.

%p
  Cards from the same custom sets that are in <a href="custom-eternal">Custom Eternal</a> are allowed. Cards from real sets are not allowed unless reprinted in one of these sets.
